text = "First we define [code]number[/code] and set it to [code]0[/code].

For each loop we;
- draw a square
- move turtlre
- add [code]1[/code] to [code]number[/code].

For as long as [code]number[/code] is less than [code]3[/code], we run the code in the while loop.

When [code]number[/code] reaches [code]3[/code], the computer exits the while loop and moves on to the next line.

Rather than copy and paste the same lines of code, we can simply alter the while loop."
